Herbert James Craig CBE (30 September 1869 – 18 March 1934) was a British Liberal Party politician, businessman and barrister.
He was born the son of James Craig MP and Kate Sophia Hould. He was educated at Rugby School and Trinity College, Cambridge. He married, in 1909, Elsie Rundall.Who Was Who
